message.text:
Hi OPC,

Thank you for your support last week. We have experienced both ups and downs, but we remain committed and will not give up. As we enter the second half of the month, we sincerely ask for your continued support to help us achieve our targets and keep our operations afloat.

Tomorrow, we will have at least 230 tubs available. I will be at the stall by 8:00 AM, and you may already reserve your food starting today. Hope you can help us get sold out by 1:30.

We truly hope for your support in helping us make it through the week. Every order makes a meaningful difference, and we are deeply grateful for your kindness.

Chicken Parmigiana - ₱120

Beside Bro Sisig and FEU FC Building (Feuture Center).
